ng if I had been just lucky or if the fact that I'm ally to CoV makes them ignoring me even if I'm clearly killing one of their friends right in from of them...<br><br>Den<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uasahiofoc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Asahi of OC</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/13/02 12:25:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=540.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Faction Good!</span><hr size=1> They like your faction...plus they don't agro for killing the wyverns.  I'm still KOS to Claws of Veeshan, but I can run my wyverns right over the top of a drake, as long as I stay out of his agro range.  If you're not KOS to Claws then you have nothing to worry about unless the drake gets caught in your AEs. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udeneteth1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Deneteth1</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/13/02 1:02:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=540.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://deneteth.freeservers.com/image/den2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Faction Good!</span><hr size=1> Good <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :D --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/happy.gif ALT=":D"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   All the more reasons to love CS...<br><br>Thanks for the answer <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udeneteth1.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Deneteth1</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_ball.gif" BORDER=0> at: 8/13/02 1:02:35 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uturielaen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Turielaen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/13/02 2:29:30 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=540.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Faction Good!</span><hr size=1> Hmm, I'm indifferent to CoV, and I'm pretty sure I got jumped by the wandering drake while quad kitting Wyverns. I'm also sure that this happened while I was running, the drake had not been hurt by my PoF. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=23101">Turielaen</a><BR>Level 51 High-Elf Channeler <BR>Founders of Honor - Terris-Thule</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/usinnjatorix.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sinnjatorix</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/14/02 4:25:40 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=540.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://w1.853.telia.com/~u85304784/pics/eq/Stringius.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Faction Good!</span><hr size=1> My necro got attacked by a cobalt drake while pulling a wyvern, was dubious at the time, and since my darkness spell is target only i could not have hit it by mistake.<br><br> <p>Sinnjatorixx dark elf wizard of the <B>8</b>th fizzle AB server<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_pr